{
  "texts": [
    "Accuracy is paramount in verifying that the recommendations are well-aligned with user preferences and feedback.",
    "To evaluate this:",
    "Direct User Ratings: Users rate the accuracy of recommendations on a defined scale.",
    "Comparison Metrics: Recommended itineraries are compared against user-actualized trips (where available) to gauge alignment.",
    "User satisfaction explores whether the generated recommendations meet or exceed user expectations."
  ]
}